ut your program is critical.\r\n\r\nKeep in mind that people interpret words differently. Scan, assessment, risk, and vulnerability have different meanings to different people and resulted in some miscommunication issues and differing expectations. Take a step back to clearly define those terms and ensure everyone is on the same page.', 'Test page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '416-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-01-14 20:18:44', '2020-01-14 14:18:44', '', 416, 'http://bangladesh-24local.com/416-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
